#--------- BACK ---------#

To launch the back, you need to run the following commands

- mix ecto.create
- mix ecto.migrate
- mix run priv/repo/seeds.exs 

Then launch the phoenix server with this command

- mix phx.server

Generic Admin user

Username : admin@admin.fr
Password : test1234!

#--------- FRONT ---------#

For the front, you need to run the following commands

- npm install
- npm run serve

#--------- DEVOPS --------#

You have 3 .gitlab-ci.yml, one in the timemanager directory, one in the app directory, one in the api directory.

You have 3 docker directory one in the timemanager directory, one in the app directory, one in the api directory. With 3 docker-compose.